      <br>Check your&nbsp;device.
    </div>
    <div align="center" id ="sms_fallback" style="display:block">
      <p>No message arrived? <br><u><a onclick="sendSms()" style="cursor: pointer;">Click to get a text message instead.</a><u></p>
